<body>

<form>
	<input type="text" placeholder ="아이디" required ="required"><br>
	<input type="email" placeholder = "test@t.t">
	<input type="tel" placeholder = "010-xxxx-xxxx">
	<hr>
	<input type="submit" value="submit">
	<input type="button" value="button">
	<button type="submit" disabled="disabled">버튼1</button>
	<button type="button">버튼2</button>
</form>
required: 필수 입력 사항이 되며 검증까지 해준다.<br>
pattern : 정규표현식을 넣어서 사용하며 \d 는 숫자의미 {n} 숫자 개수의미<br>
readonly : 읽기전용<br>
disabled : 비활성화<br>

<h3>label</h3>
- input, textarea, select들의 제목을 넣는 태그
<form action="">
	<fieldset>
	<legend>취미조사</legend>
	<input id="id"><br><!--id 현재페이지 값, name 다음페이지 값을전달  -->
	<label for="h1">책읽기</label>
	<input type="checkbox" value="1" name="hobby" id="h1">
	<label>멍타기</label>
	<input type="checkbox" value="2" name="hobby">
	<label>게임</label>
	<input type="checkbox"value="3" name="hobby">
	<label for ="id">아이디</label>
	</fieldset>
	<input type="submit" value="전송">
	
</form>
	<form method="get">	
		<label style="background: beige;">aaa</label>
		10대 <input type="radio" value="10" name="age">
		20대 <input type="radio" value="20" name="age">		
		<br>
		<select size="1" name="test">
			<option value="apple">사과
			<option>수박
			<option>딸기
		</select>
		<input type="submit" value="submit">
	</form>



<form action="ex06.html">
	<input type="text" name="name" placeholder="input name"><br>
	<input type="text" name="addr" placeholder="input address"><br>
	<textarea rows = "3" name="con" cols = "50" placeholder="내용"></textarea><br>
	<input type="reset" value="초기화">
	<input type="submit" value="전송">
	<input type="button" value="버튼">
</form>

<hr>
	10대 <input type="checkbox" name="age" checked="checked">
	20대 <input type="checkbox" name="age" >
	30대 <input type="checkbox" name="age" >
	40대 <input type="checkbox" name="age" >


<hr>
	10대 <input type="radio" name="age" checked="checked">
	20대 <input type="radio" name="age" >
	40대 <input type="radio" name="age11" >
	50대 <input type="radio" name="age11" >
	
<hr>
	<h3>input</h3>
	- 데이터를 입력받는 태그<br>
	- type속성에 따라 형식이 달라진다<br>
	<input type="button" value="버 튼"><br>
	<input type="submit" value="서브밋"><br>
	<input type="reset" value="초기화"><br>
	<input type="image" value="img.jpg" width="50"><br>
	<input type="file"><br>
	
	<input type="text" value="값 입력"><br>
	<input type="password" value="비밀번호"><br>
	<input type="email" placeholder="text@test.t"><br>
	<input type="search" value="값 입력시x버튼 생성"><br>
	<input type="tel" value="010-555-555"><br>
	<input type="number" min="1" max="10" value="1"><br>
	
	<input type="color"><br>
	<input type="range"><br>
	<input type="radio"><br>
	<input type="checkbox"><br>
	<input type="hidden" value="값을 숨김"><br>
	<input type="text" value="읽기전용" readonly="readonly"><br>

